
& unit_purchase
 
 >> Help: Unit Purchase (Economy Commands)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Syntax: unit
 Syntax: unitpl
 Syntax: unitbuy <mech_ref>
 Syntax: unitsell <mech_ref>
 Syntax: unitestimate <mech_ref>
 Syntax: unitnewpl
 Syntax: unitoffer <player>/<mech_ref>/<XP>
 
 The 'unit' command in its various froms help manage the buying and selling of
 your permanent units. These commands are centered around your purchase list,
 or PL ('help PL').
 
 NOTE: Most of these commands must be done from a spawn room.
 
{ 'help unit_purchase2' for more }
 
